{"tid":2156914,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"請珍惜美斯","createTime":"2020-08-14T19:13:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-14T19:49:05.000Z","uid":9710,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"ce7efef455e412a3f0ed8ed02663be1693365d0c","tid":2156914,"uid":9710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T19:13:26.000Z","msg":"細個開始睇波果陣好拎憎疤狗，覺得沙維小白影帝成撚日插水（當年影帝扮痛偷睇），Tikitaka進攻次次都好似教科書一樣既戰術好悶<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n到佢地退晒休，先知果D老練既技術／走位係好野黎<br />\n<br />\n沙維既獨特節奏、小白（全盛時期）既First Step、影帝對插水既執著，都係到退休／收左皮先發現佢地原來咁拎勁<br />\n<br />\n高登仔好多人都反美斯，但係老實講佢既Foot Work技術、入球能力、對比賽既執著，冇人比得上佢（我覺得依家Messi&gt;&gt;朗拿度）<br />\n<br />\n我諗美斯最多都係打多幾年就退休，其實睇得1場得1場，好好珍惜<br />\n<br />\n美斯今季四大皆空<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04c479bce2d288a35ded14cd8384df2a42f19e29","tid":2156914,"uid":20522,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T19:49:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZtRpQct.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZtRpQct.jpg&h=ef8fead1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n樓主部ps4用唔著<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}